Okay.

163
00:11:15,624 --> 00:11:19,676
Lift you up, lift you up~

164
00:11:22,832 --> 00:11:23,463
Let's work hard together.

165
00:11:23,464 --> 00:11:25,400
One day, we have to go to Cannes together.

166
00:11:31,100 --> 00:11:32,100
What the heck?

167
00:11:35,500 --> 00:11:37,000
What is this?

168
00:11:37,300 --> 00:11:38,300
A chaotic scene?

169
00:11:55,500 --> 00:11:57,038
Here he goes again...

170
00:11:58,290 --> 00:12:00,194
What was that scene just now?

171
00:12:00,195 --> 00:12:02,100
That “lifted up high” scene.

172
00:12:04,100 --> 00:12:06,788
Seeing Hajime from the
lifted-up perspective is basically

173
00:12:06,812 --> 00:12:09,500
like having a front-row seat
in the rock zone at a concert.

174
00:12:10,700 --> 00:12:11,838
Damn it!

175
00:12:12,538 --> 00:12:15,575
