197
00:13:42,900 --> 00:13:46,100
Akafuji, no, Shuichiro!

198
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:48,000
Awesome!

199
00:13:50,200 --> 00:13:51,600
Everyone, give a round of applause.

200
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:53,200
Okay.

201
00:13:59,400 --> 00:14:00,085
