help but say it when I saw your smile.

231
00:15:51,000 --> 00:15:52,800
Akafuji, you really are interesting.

232
00:15:54,200 --> 00:15:55,200
Hajime.

233
00:15:55,700 --> 00:15:56,247
What's wrong?

234
00:15:56,647 --> 00:15:59,000
What kind of relationship
do you have with Mr. Haibara?

235
00:15:59,342 --> 00:16:01,240
Is your relationship close
enough that you'd let each

236
00:16:01,264 --> 00:16:03,382
other do something like
lifting each other up in the air?

237
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:08,000
No, I'm just glad it suits your taste.

238
00:16:24,800 --> 00:16:26,300
Um... Mr. Akafuji.

239
00:16:28,800 --> 00:16:30,300
Tomorrow's your day off, right?

240
00:16:31,100 --> 00:16:32,100
Yeah.

241
00:16:33,400 --> 00:16:34,400
