242
00:16:37,400 --> 00:16:38,840
Would you like to stay over tonight?

243
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:42,400
Is that okay?

244
00:16:43,500 --> 00:16:44,500
Of course you can.

245
00:16:45,700 --> 00:16:47,600
Then I'll gladly accept your invitation.

246
00:17:14,300 --> 00:17:15,300
Hajime.

247
00:17:18,500 --> 00:17:19,500
Mr. Akafuji.

248
00:18:00,200 --> 00:18:01,200
Good night.

249
00:18:08,800 --> 00:18:09,800
Hajime?

250
00:18:12,400 --> 00:18:13,600
